Numbering

If a curious reader were to ask the reference to the most used and probably the most famousChaupai: मंगल भवन अमंगल हारी। द्रवउ सो दसरथ अष्िर बबहारी।। (Mangal Bhavan AmangalHaari | Drabahu Su Dasharath Achar Bihari) the answer will be that it is the 2nd line of the second Chaupai after Doha Number 111 in Bal Kānd. … Source: TW
